---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="MEMBERSHIP MILESTONE: AARBAA Reaches 15,000 Members - AARBAA">
  <section class="news-article" style="padding-top: 120px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          <!-- Article Header -->
          <header class="article-header mb-5">
            <div class="text-center">
              <span class="badge bg-success text-uppercase mb-3" style="font-size: 0.875rem; letter-spacing: 1px;">MILESTONE ACHIEVEMENT</span>
              <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3" style="color: #0A3161; line-height: 1.2;">
                MEMBERSHIP MILESTONE: AARBAA Reaches 15,000 Members
              </h1>
              <div class="article-meta text-muted">
                <span><i class="far fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i>December 10, 2024</span>
                <span class="mx-3">|</span>
                <span><i class="far fa-user me-2"></i>AARBAA Leadership Team</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </header>

          <!-- Hero Image -->
          <div class="article-hero mb-5" style="position: relative; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
            <img src="/images/victory.jpg" alt="AARBAA members celebrating" style="width: 100%; height: auto;">
            <div style="position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.8), transparent); padding: 2rem;">
              <p class="text-white mb-0 fw-bold">AARBAA members gather to celebrate reaching 15,000 strong</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Article Content -->
          <article class="article-content">
            <div class="lead-paragraph mb-4" style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333;">
              <p>In a testament to growing frustration with cyclist entitlement across America, AARBAA has officially surpassed 15,000 members, marking a 300% increase in membership over the past year alone. This milestone reflects a nationwide awakening to the need for cyclist accountability and road safety reform.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Celebration Banner -->
            <div class="celebration-banner text-center my-5 p-5" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A3161 0%, #B31942 100%); color: white; border-radius: 1rem; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
              <div style="position: absolute; top: -50px; left: -50px; width: 150px; height: 150px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%;"></div>
              <div style="position: absolute; bottom: -30px; right: -30px; width: 100px; height: 100px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 50%;"></div>
              <h2 class="display-1 fw-bold mb-3" style="text-shadow: 3px 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);">15,000</h2>
              <p class="lead mb-0">STRONG AND GROWING!</p>
            </div>

            <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3" style="color: #B31942;">The Growth Story</h2>
            <p>What started as a small group of concerned citizens in Denver has exploded into a nationwide movement. AARBAA chapters now operate in 47 states, with new branches opening weekly. Our message resonates with millions of Americans who are tired of cyclist privilege and ready for change.</p>

            <!-- Growth Timeline -->
            <div class="timeline my-5">
              <h3 class="mb-4">Our Journey to 15,000</h3>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px;">
                <h5 class="text-primary">January 2023 - Founded</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">12 founding members meet in Denver garage</p>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px;">
                <h5 class="text-primary">March 2023 - 500 Members</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">First viral video exposes cyclist road rage incident</p>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px;">
                <h5 class="text-primary">July 2023 - 2,500 Members</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">National media coverage begins</p>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px;">
                <h5 class="text-primary">November 2023 - 5,000 Members</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">First legislative victory with local bike lane restrictions</p>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px;">
                <h5 class="text-primary">April 2024 - 10,000 Members</h5>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">AARBAA recognized as legitimate advocacy organization</p>
              </div>
              <div class="timeline-item mb-4 p-3" style="border-left: 3px solid #B31942; margin-left: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
                <h5 class="text-danger">December 2024 - 15,000 Members!</h5>
                <p class="mb-0 fw-bold">Fastest growing road safety organization in America</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Member Demographics -->
            <div class="demographics-section my-5 p-4" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
              <h3 class="mb-4">Who Are Our Members?</h3>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <h5>By Profession:</h5>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Working Commuters: 42%</li>
                    <li>Parents & Caregivers: 28%</li>
                    <li>Commercial Drivers: 15%</li>
                    <li>Law Enforcement: 8%</li>
                    <li>Other: 7%</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                  <h5>By Region:</h5>
                  <ul>
                    <li>West Coast: 31%</li>
                    <li>Mountain States: 24%</li>
                    <li>Midwest: 20%</li>
                    <li>Northeast: 15%</li>
                    <li>South: 10%</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Member Testimonials -->
            <h2 class="mt-5 mb-4" style="color: #B31942;">What Our Members Say</h2>
            
            <div class="testimonial-card mb-4 p-4" style="background-color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
              <p class="mb-3" style="font-style: italic;">"AARBAA gave me a voice. For years, I've been frustrated by cyclists ignoring traffic laws, but I felt powerless. Now I'm part of a movement that's actually making a difference."</p>
              <p class="mb-0 text-muted"><strong>- Jennifer K., Phoenix, AZ</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card mb-4 p-4" style="background-color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
              <p class="mb-3" style="font-style: italic;">"As a commercial driver, I deal with reckless cyclists daily. AARBAA's advocacy for mandatory cyclist insurance could save my career if an accident happens."</p>
              <p class="mb-0 text-muted"><strong>- Mike T., Chicago, IL</strong></p>
            </div>

            <div class="testimonial-card mb-4 p-4" style="background-color: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 0.5rem; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
              <p class="mb-3" style="font-style: italic;">"The cyclist lobby has had too much power for too long. AARBAA is finally providing balance to the conversation about road safety and infrastructure."</p>
              <p class="mb-0 text-muted"><strong>- David L., Portland, OR</strong></p>
            </div>

            <!-- Impact Section -->
            <div class="impact-section my-5 p-5" style="background-color: #0A3161; color: white; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
              <h3 class="text-center mb-4">Our Impact So Far</h3>
              <div class="row text-center">
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                  <h4 class="display-4">23</h4>
                  <p>Cities with AARBAA-influenced cyclist regulations</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                  <h4 class="display-4">$2.3M</h4>
                  <p>Raised for road safety advocacy</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                  <h4 class="display-4">156</h4>
                  <p>Media appearances nationwide</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 mb-4">
                  <h4 class="display-4">47</h4>
                  <p>States with active chapters</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3" style="color: #B31942;">What's Next?</h2>
            <p>With 15,000 members and growing, AARBAA is positioned to make even greater impacts in 2025:</p>
            
            <ul class="future-plans mb-5">
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Federal Legislation:</strong> Push for the Cyclist Accountability Act at the national level</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Insurance Reform:</strong> Partner with insurance companies to develop cyclist liability policies</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Education Campaigns:</strong> Launch nationwide "Share Responsibly" awareness programs</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Legal Support:</strong> Establish fund for motorists unfairly blamed in cyclist accidents</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><strong>Technology Solutions:</strong> Develop app for real-time cyclist violation reporting</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Join CTA -->
            <div class="join-cta text-center p-5 my-5" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #B31942 0%, #0A3161 100%); color: white; border-radius: 1rem;">
              <h3 class="mb-4">Be Part of the Movement</h3>
              <p class="lead mb-4">Help us reach 25,000 members by 2025. Together, we can restore sanity to American roads.</p>
              <div class="d-grid gap-2 d-md-flex justify-content-md-center">
                <a href="/join" class="btn btn-light btn-lg px-5 me-md-2">Join AARBAA Today</a>
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-lg px-5">Get Involved</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Acknowledgments -->
            <div class="acknowledgments mt-5 p-4" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 0.5rem;">
              <h4 class="mb-3">Special Thanks</h4>
              <p>To our founding members, chapter leaders, volunteers, and every single member who has made this milestone possible. Your dedication to road safety and common sense makes America's roads safer for everyone.</p>
              <p class="mb-0 text-muted text-center"><em>Here's to the next 15,000!</em></p>
            </div>

            <!-- Related Articles -->
            <div class="related-articles mt-5 pt-5 border-top">
              <h3 class="mb-4">Related Articles</h3>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                  <a href="/news/operation-rush-hour" class="text-decoration-none">
                    <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-primary">OPERATION RUSH HOUR: Exposing Cyclist Traffic Violations</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted">Groundbreaking investigation reveals shocking violation rates...</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                  <a href="/news/city-council-presentation" class="text-decoration-none">
                    <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <h5 class="card-title text-primary">City Council Presentation Success</h5>
                        <p class="card-text text-muted">AARBAA presents compelling case for cyclist regulation...</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .timeline-item {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 30px;
    }
    
    .timeline-item::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      left: -8px;
      top: 0;
      width: 15px;
      height: 15px;
      background-color: #B31942;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 3px solid white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px #B31942;
    }
    
    .testimonial-card {
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    
    .testimonial-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2) !important;
    }
  </style>
</MainLayout>